# Line-ending normalization. Without this, git autocrlf=true checks .mjs files
# out as CRLF in fresh worktrees, and vitest's transform chokes on a CRLF-
# terminated `#!` shebang ("Invalid or unexpected token"), breaking the gate.
# The committed blobs are already LF; this keeps working copies LF too.
*.mjs text eol=lf
